titleStmt.title: Orders to be observed while His Majestie, or the two Houses of Parliament continue in Oxford agreed upon by the vice-chancellor and delegates, to be communicated to the heads of houses, and by them to their respective companies.
titleStmt.author: University of Oxford.

notesStmt.note: Manuscript note: "These ord's were printed 7. March (Munday) 1680. & forthwith sent to the colleges & halls, to be posted up."
Place and date of publication suggested by Wing (2nd ed.).
Reproduction of original in the Bodleian Library.
